transArray.content: The hotel environment is very good, the transportation is convenient, and the breakfast is rich. You can do nucleic acid tests at the door, which is very convenient. The ladies and brothers at the front desk have very good service attitude, especially when I ordered several takeaways, they were arranged to be delivered to my room. There are not enough robots. If you use it, send it to us personally...
Dear guest, thank you very much for choosing. Summer has the late glow. Just like the little guy who comes late, everyone is smiling. I love you, little guy.
